{{Flavour|Blinks allies in sight of the caster away from a nearby enemy.}}

'''Blink Allies Away''' is a monster-only spell which causes all allies of the caster to [[blink]], always placing them farther away from the player than they were beforehand.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Blink Allies Away was added in [[0.14]].

